Package neqsim.blackoil

Class BlackOilPVTTable

java.lang.Object
neqsim.blackoil.BlackOilPVTTable
public class BlackOilPVTTable extends Object
Black-Oil PVT table with linear interpolation in pressure. Units (recommended): P: bar (or Pa, but be consistent across inputs!) Rs: Sm3 gas / Sm3 oil Rv: Sm3 oil / Sm3 gas (often 0.0) Bo, Bg, Bw: reservoir m3 per standard m3 (rm3 / Sm3) mu_*: PaÂ·s

esol
